[normal]EPSRC IRC Submission of Evidence to the House of Commons Science &amp; Technology [bold]Select Committee Inquiry into Antimicrobial Resistance [bold]6
[normal]th
[normal] November 2013.
[normal]&#xa0;[bold]1.0 [bold]Executive [bold]Summary[bold] 
